it was 1989, '90.

15:41.357 --> 15:44.235
<i>Gianni's mom and I
were going through</i>

15:44.318 --> 15:47.905
<i>a really hard time
and we split up,</i>

15:47.989 --> 15:50.074
<i>and I don't want
to get into details,</i>

15:50.158 --> 15:52.410
<i>but I never forget
this friggin' guy</i>

15:52.493 --> 15:55.079
<i>sittin' across from me
and saying,</i>

15:55.163 --> 15:58.332
"You realize you're never gonna
see your kids again, right?"

15:58.416 --> 16:00.543
And it was like, boom.

16:01.794 --> 16:03.796
Sound. Be ready.

16:03.880 --> 16:05.715
( power tool whirs )

16:05.798 --> 16:08.593
<i>I'm from that generation of men</i>

16:08.676 --> 16:09.927
<i>where you didn't go to therapy.</i>

16:10.011 --> 16:12.305
<i>When you got
into those places,</i>

16:12.388 --> 16:14.140
<i>you just friggin'
toughed it out.</i>

16:14.223 --> 16:16.559
But you know what?
It doesn't always work that way.

16:16.642 --> 16:21.272
When you're in crisis,
when you're in that state,

16:21.355 --> 16:23.858
you have to find a way
to ask for help.

16:23.941 --> 16:26.903
You have to find a way
to get yourself into

16:26.986 --> 16:29.280
a safe environment
with professionals,

16:29.363 --> 16:32.742
and there's people out there
that will help you

16:32.825 --> 16:35.036
take one foot
in front of the other.

16:35.119 --> 16:36.245
Yeah, it takes
a lot of courage.

16:36.329 --> 16:37.580
It takes guts.

16:37.663 --> 16:39.582
<i>And on some level
I have a lot of guilt,</i>

16:39.665 --> 16:41.459
<i>and I think sometimes
my behavior</i>

16:41.542 --> 16:44.253
<i>in what I did at that time,</i>

16:44.337 --> 16:45.671
<i>when I hurt myself‐‐</i>

16:45.755 --> 16:47.465
<i>Gianni was like
seven years old.</i>

16:47.548 --> 16:50.551
<i>I made mistakes, man,
I did some things,</i>

16:50.635 --> 16:52.595
<i>and I can't take
any of it back,</i>

16:52.678 --> 16:54.805
<i>but I realize,
you know what,</i>

16:54.889 --> 16:58.059
<i>it's just part of
what's happened in my life.</i>

17:01.145 --> 17:04.815
Gianni:
