18:00.621 --> 18:02.206
<i>in the moment of creating,</i>

18:02.290 --> 18:04.166
<i>no matter what
your mental state is,</i>

18:04.250 --> 18:06.919
<i>there's some magical
machination</i>

18:07.003 --> 18:09.422
<i>that happens in the moment
of doing something.</i>

18:09.505 --> 18:11.424
<i>Whether you're hitting the keys
on the piano,</i>

18:11.507 --> 18:13.426
<i>whether you're a dancer and
you're in the moment of flight,</i>

18:13.509 --> 18:15.720
<i>whether you're hitting
the canvas for the first time,</i>

18:15.803 --> 18:17.888
<i>and it's just
that movement of the brush</i>

18:17.972 --> 18:19.432
on the canvas.

18:19.515 --> 18:21.559
In that moment,
that's where it is,

18:21.642 --> 18:22.935
that's where it's at.

