18:31.402 --> 18:33.904
Gianni:
<i>No matter what my state is,</i>

18:33.988 --> 18:35.573
<i>I can go to that
and have that</i>

18:35.656 --> 18:37.199
as my, like‐‐ phtt!‐‐

18:37.283 --> 18:38.909
centered, boom,
know what to do.

18:38.993 --> 18:40.870
<i>That's the gratifying thing,</i>

18:40.953 --> 18:42.413
<i>that's why I do art.</i>

18:42.496 --> 18:45.207
<i>There's restraint
and pause</i>

18:45.291 --> 18:46.709
<i>and peace now,</i>

18:46.792 --> 18:48.794
<i>where I can go to a work,</i>

18:48.878 --> 18:50.463
<i>work on it,</i>

18:50.546 --> 18:53.007
<i>feel that it's OK
