19:34.715 --> 19:38.552
And now I kinda like the piece,
looking at it a year later.

19:38.636 --> 19:40.763
<i>But in the time,
I was just so angry</i>

19:40.846 --> 19:42.973
<i>I just felt like,
"This is foreign to me,</i>

19:43.057 --> 19:45.226
<i>I don't know what to do,"
but you persist,</i>

19:45.309 --> 19:48.062
<i>you continue to do your craft
a little bit each day.</i>

19:48.145 --> 19:50.564
<i>And if you really love it,
you're gonna be
inherently consistent</i>

19:50.648 --> 19:52.525
because you're gonna
want to do it each day.

19:52.608 --> 19:54.694
<i>And the results are gonna vary,</i>

19:54.777 --> 19:57.738
<i>but process is king‐‐
stay in the process.</i>

19:57.822 --> 19:59.240
<i>Stay in the process.</i>

