21:38.339 --> 21:42.134
I, uh, caused
a lot of wreckage

21:42.218 --> 21:43.594
and a lot of pain

21:43.677 --> 21:45.346
and a lot of chaos.

21:45.429 --> 21:49.183
<i>And I'm still
a work in progress, you know,</i>

21:49.266 --> 21:51.101
<i>I'm still really new to this.</i>

21:51.185 --> 21:53.604
<i>But a lot's changed
over the course of the year</i>

21:53.687 --> 21:55.606
<i>because I put in
