22:00.194 --> 22:03.739
<i>And my living amends
to my dad</i>

22:03.823 --> 22:05.950
<i>is to grant him
peace of mind.</i>

22:06.033 --> 22:07.618
<i>It's a lifetime of work,</i>

22:07.701 --> 22:09.578
<i>and it's something
I get to practice‐‐</i>

22:09.662 --> 22:13.082
<i>I have the opportunity
to practice each day.</i>

22:15.042 --> 22:18.504
Jimmy:
<i>I had to, like, learn
about patience, acceptance,</i>

22:18.587 --> 22:20.714
<i>those things
that really test you.</i>

22:20.798 --> 22:22.591
<i>You say you love somebody,
