22:22.675 --> 22:24.802
but until you're in that arena

22:24.885 --> 22:26.679
and you're wrestling
with those beasts and stuff,

22:26.762 --> 22:29.139
that's where you find out
where your character's at.

22:29.223 --> 22:30.891
<i>You know,
at the end of the day,</i>

22:30.975 --> 22:32.560
<i>he's someone that needs help,
he's sick.</i>

22:32.643 --> 22:34.436
<i>I gotta figure out a way
to have a relationship,</i>

22:34.520 --> 22:36.021
<i>but have a boundary,</i>

22:36.105 --> 22:37.898
<i>that I can protect myself
and take care of myself</i>

22:37.982 --> 22:40.693
<i>and my wife and my family.</i>

22:46.156 --> 22:49.451
<i>You know,
maybe part of the thing
about doing this thing</i>

22:49.535 --> 22:51.662
<i>is that I'm hoping,
when somebody sees this,</i>

22:51.745 --> 22:54.331
<i>is that yeah,
there's a lot of pain,</i>

22:54.415 --> 22:56.458
<i>there's a lot of scars,
there's a lot of wounding,</i>

22:56.542 --> 22:58.961
<i>but you know, there is healing
and there is‐‐</i>

22:59.044 --> 23:01.672
<i>there's a light
at the end of the tunnel.</i>

23:01.755 --> 23:06.135
But you gotta do the work,
you gotta do the time.

23:06.218 --> 23:09.680
